snippet: Russell Wilson will visit the Rangers’ training camp a month after leading the Seattle Seahawks to their first title.
abstract: MLB Roundup; Seattle Seahawks quarterback Russell Wilson will revisit his baseball past as a Texas Rangers prospect by visiting training camp a month after leading Seahawks to their first Super Bowl title; other new noted.
